article_title: Adoption case ends at U.S. Supreme Court

article_metadata.description: A widely publicized adoption case involving a Carthage couple and a Guatemalan mother living in Carthage illegally has ended after more than six years at the U.S. Supreme Court.
article_metadata.author: John Hacker
